data.description: Welcome to your new home located at 6531 SW 107TH ST, OCALA in the highly sought out 55+ community of Spruce Creek – This delightful home boasts a fantastic location, a fenced yard for added privacy, and significant upgrades that ensure modern living. The home offers three bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a screened lanai, a covered front & back porch, and a workshop that you can enter from undercover. The kitchen is ready for you to make some memorable meals with stainless steel appliances. Share your meal with family and friends with plenty of room to entertain.  Situated in a highly desirable area and nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac, this residence offers easy access to local amenities and entertainment options. Enjoy the convenience of being centrally located while still enjoying the tranquility of a residential neighborhood.    The property features a fenced yard, providing a secure and secluded space for relaxation, play, and entertaining. Where you can simply enjoy outdoor activities or plant a garden, this feature adds an extra layer of privacy to your home.      This home offers a perfect blend of functionality and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours! Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm and convenience of 6531 SW 107TH ST, OCALA. Your dream home awaits!
